The '''G-12 Power blaster''' was a heavy [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] designed by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] to combat the [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] of [[the Colony]]. They were used by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] and [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] during [[Battle of Sarm]] in the [[Swarm War]]. Unlike a typical [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]], the G-12 required a separate, dedicated [[Power cell/Legends|power pack]].

